DESCRIPTION=" The ASS format can be used for extremely complex subtitles. Text can be rendered with borders and shadows in arbitrary colors, with alpha transparency and arbitrarily positioned. Additionally, various vectors transformations (rotations, shearing, scaling) and bitmap operations (box blur, gaussian blur) can be applied. Finally, it is also possible to clip resulting subtitles. There are even more advanced features available, like vector drawings, vector blending and animations."
